column2: SELECT s.SpecObjID, s.z, s.fiberMag_r, s.sn_#, L.ew, L.sigma, L.sigmaErr, K.ew, K.sigma, K.sigmaErr into mydb.Coupled2 from SpecObj as s, SpecLine as L, SpecLine as K WHERE    (L.LineID = #)    and (K.LineID = #)    and s.SpecObjID = L.specObjID    and L.specObjID = K.specObjID   and L.ew/nullif(L.ewErr,#)>#   and s.z >#   and s.sn_# > # ORDER BY s.mag_#
